replies.author: z97615669
replies.txt_content:
在 Ender IO config

eplacewitherskeletons {

    # Separates wither and normal skeletons into different entities, enables the powered spawner to treat them differently [EXPERIMENTAL - MAY CAUSE ISSUES WITH OTHER MODS]

    B:Misc=false

}

给你提供下这个参考
http://www.minecraftforge.net/fo ... or-console-spamlag/

这个是导致线程卡死的主要原因

replies.author: z97615669
replies.txt_content:
然后优化下给你
然后找到在config目录下的forge.cfg打开
找到
    B:removeErroringEntities=false
    B:removeErroringTileEntities=false
修改成
    B:removeErroringEntities=true
    B:removeErroringTileEntities=true
# Summary / TL;DR:

## I am having Console Spam errors, causing 100% CPU & RAM useage, and lag spikes every 10-15 seconds. As far as I can tell it's from a chunk loading/entity tracker error somewhere.

这个垃圾信息会导致主线程卡死
